00:06:13.240 --> 00:06:17.240
No, don't leave. I won't tell him. What's going on?

00:06:17.240 --> 00:06:21.240
Well, no, I really shouldn't tell you.

00:06:21.240 --> 00:06:23.240
You could trust me.

00:06:23.240 --> 00:06:27.240
It's just...Centra Gwelod is in trouble.

00:06:27.240 --> 00:06:31.240
Our fields seem to be producing less and less these days.

00:06:31.240 --> 00:06:37.240
We had to sacrifice our servants' food for two days to be able to provide this feast.

00:06:37.240 --> 00:06:40.240
And our army's getting weaker and weaker.

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:43.240
We have so few men left.

00:06:43.240 --> 00:06:46.240
Really? I had no idea.

00:06:46.240 --> 00:06:50.240
I'm just so worried that soon someone might invade us.

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:54.240
And whoever it was, I suppose I'd have to marry them.

00:06:54.240 --> 00:06:57.240
What if it's a monster of a man?

00:06:57.240 --> 00:07:01.240
That would be awful. Is there any way I can help?

00:07:01.240 --> 00:07:07.240
Well, I did wonder. No, you wouldn't do that. Ignore me.

00:07:07.240 --> 00:07:10.240
No, tell me. I want to help.

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:16.240
Well, it's just, if you were to invade, you'd surely succeed, wouldn't you?

00:07:16.240 --> 00:07:20.240
And I wouldn't mind marrying you.

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:24.240
I know you'd care for our people, put us back on track.

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:28.240
But I couldn't do that. Your father trusts me.

00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:31.240
Well, you might be saving us from worse.

00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:33.240
Well...

00:07:33.240 --> 00:07:36.240
Oh, please, please save our kingdom.

00:07:36.240 --> 00:07:40.240
Oh, well. If it's to save the kingdom, then...

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:44.240
All right, let's meet later to plan things in detail.

00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:48.240
But I'd better go now and drink some wine with the King before he gets suspicious.

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:55.240
Yes! Well, that was easy.

00:07:55.240 --> 00:07:59.240
