00:10:15.240 --> 00:10:20.240
Shall I tell the king who betrayed him? Tell him it was his own daughter.

00:10:20.240 --> 00:10:26.240
I know he wants to know. Maybe. Maybe I could use it as a bargaining chip.

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:29.240
Maybe he'll let me go free if I tell him.

00:10:29.240 --> 00:10:33.240
While Rodri schemes, Mereyd knows her life hangs in the balance.

00:10:33.240 --> 00:10:41.240
So now it's all over. My plan has failed. I don't know what to do. My father's going to find out what I've done.

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:47.240
Rodri will tell him. Will he show me mercy? Does he even know how?

00:10:47.240 --> 00:10:51.240
