00:10:51.240 --> 00:10:58.240
I just felt so trapped, so burdened by duty. But there must have been a better way.

00:10:58.240 --> 00:11:06.240
It didn't feel like there was. What about free will? Where was my free will?

00:11:06.240 --> 00:11:15.240
I need to fix this. How can I? How can I keep my father from finding out what I've done?

00:11:15.240 --> 00:11:21.240
What if? What if I didn't do my duty at the well today?

00:11:21.240 --> 00:11:27.240
Just to see what the spirit will do. If the curse will really fall.

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:35.240
Maybe if the curse falls, whatever it is, in all the confusion, Rodri won't tell my father about me.

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:44.240
Or maybe Rodri will die. Or my father will die. Or will I die? After all, I've nothing to lose.

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:52.240
