00:12:00.240 --> 00:12:08.240
Hmm. What a sly little thing you've turned out to be. I guess I should have seen it coming. You've always resented me.

00:12:08.240 --> 00:12:16.240
Carrying your buckets again this evening, are you? They must be heavier than ever today. Do you feel your back begin to break?

00:12:16.240 --> 00:12:21.240
The weight of all that guilt? The tears and pain you've brought to my people?

00:12:21.240 --> 00:12:30.240
Well, you forced my hand. When you've finished your duties tonight, I will have my soldiers seize you. I will punish you.

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:37.240
