00:14:06.240 --> 00:14:12.240
Grandad! Grandad, where are you? Oh, you silly old wretch!

00:14:12.240 --> 00:14:15.240
Come on, Grandad, you have to get out of here!

00:14:15.240 --> 00:14:19.240
