00:14:19.240 --> 00:14:23.240
Grandad, this soaks! We have to go or we'll drown!

00:14:23.240 --> 00:14:32.240
Aye, I've got wet feet, but I'm not moving until I finish this pint. I am staying here until I finish what I've started.

00:14:36.240 --> 00:14:40.240
